Properties.Property: Desired Inventory level after a purchase reorder

Module.name: Form_Inventory List
Module.Section: Private Sub cmdPurchase_Click() If Not Me![Qty To Reorder] > 0 Then MsgBoxOKOnly NoNeedToRestock ElseIf Inventory.RestockProduct(Me![Product ID]) Then Me.Requery MsgBoxOKOnly RestockSuccess Else MsgBoxOKOnly RestockingFailed End If End Sub
